        "Title": "Making Room for a Sax Dungeon",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ELEGANT_LLAMA",
        "PublicId": "131101078482",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/elegant/scene_llama.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 9514999b-766c-4eef-8e42-9b16279bebdb).Image",
        "Description": "Agent 47, your mission is to take out Aron Ford Jr., a furry lawyer, because he&apos;s been taking up too much space in his mom&apos;s basement and she wants it for a secret sax dungeon. Also, simultaneously, Aron wants his ex-wife Valentina Yates and her new sugar zaddy Don Yates gone because he was angry they took away his hetnai collection. So to kill three birds with one stone, just do it all in one, like a package deal. I&apos;ll leave you to, 47.",
